77
00:12:59,196 --> 00:13:00,739
Pronunciei direito?

78
00:13:00,822 --> 00:13:01,865
Mousa.

79
00:13:06,578 --> 00:13:07,579
Mousa.

80
00:13:08,413 --> 00:13:09,706
